{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4f5a0a13c3","title":"中共中央批准北京市委为1976年“天安门事件”平反","origin":"根据文件原件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"03fa52cf0c","index":0,"year":1978,"month":11,"day":14,"articleId":"4f5a0a13c3"}],"tags":[{"id":"33b85cb7de","name":"四人帮","type":"人物"},{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"aa9434abe4","name":"北京文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"1e57b2696b","type":"title","text":"中共中央批准北京市委为１９７６年“天安门事件”平反","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4f5a0a13c3"},{"id":"f4ef720bbe","type":"paragraph","text":"１１月１４日，北京市为１９７６年“天安门事件”平反。经中共中央政治局常委批准，中共北京市委决定如下：","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4f5a0a13c3"},{"id":"9af9dbd880","type":"subtitle","text":"北京市委关于为天安门事件平反的决定","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4f5a0a13c3"},{"id":"8f9eb00310","type":"subtitle","text":"1978.11.14","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4f5a0a13c3"},{"id":"d075bc0638","type":"paragraph","text":"1976年清明节，广大群众到天安门广场沉痛悼念敬爱的周恩来，愤怒声讨“四人帮”，完全是革命行动。因参加此事件而被捕的三百三十八人中没有一个人是反革命。对于因悼念周恩来、反对“四人帮”，而受到迫害的同志，一律平反，恢复名誉。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4f5a0a13c3"}],"page":{"id":"151ec54192","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4f5a0a13c3","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}